{
  "Name": "Dave's Junior V3.6 (5.5x3)",
  "Description": "
      
  ------------------------------
        RELEASE VERSION: 3.6
  ------------------------------
  
  * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * 
  ***     Host requires CD2 update 18 or newer      ***
  * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *
  
  This difficulty uses Darth's 'Actual Hazard 5.5x2' difficulty as a base, but includes many features
  from Dave's Double (wavespawners, elite guards, etc.) with 50% more bugs (5.5x3)

  True Haz 5.5x3 plus:
  --------------------
  - Grunt/Web/Acid (70%/15%/15%) WaveSpawner on 80s interval
    - Starts at 20s for most missios, 300s for PE, 200s for Refinery/Salvage
    - Difficulty = ((-20 + (60 * DwarvesAmmo)) * (1.25 [if depo nitra >= 180]))
    - Stopped if anyone is down
  - Menace/Grabber/Goober/Bulk (32%/32%/32%/4%) WaveSpawner on 100s interval
    - Starts at 20s for most missions, 300s for PE, 200s for Refinery/Salvage
    - Difficulty = 1
    - Stopped if anyone is down
  - Headbounces removed for CD2 enjoyers 
  - StationaryDifficulty upped from (175-225) to (225-250)
    - StationaryDifficulty reduced (150-175) for all hot drop missions (Egg/Refinery/PE/DeepScan)
  - StationaryEnemyCount/Diversity upped from (5-6 & 3-5) to (7-7 & 7-7)
  - ECM * 1.2, 1.3, 1.1 DuringExtraction for Default, PE, and Salvage
  - Refinery ECM is increased slightly during certain phases, RefiningStalled is the largest @ 15%
  - Younglings/Stalkers removed+
  - Trash Breeder Jr. (denoted by Elite status) added to enemy pool, bulk rarity
  - VeteranLarge (Oppressors) chance left unchanged, but swaps to 0 if 2 or more Opps exist
  - Speed boost (+0.25) given to bugs DuringDillevator
  - Barragers: SpawnAmountModifier: 0.5 MaxSpawnCount: 1 (2) - 0 (1) for Escort Only
  - Leeches copied from Double, with 75% speed
  - Added elite leeches, slow and slightly tankier with a long reach
  - Exploders replaced with variable speed exploders @ 0.8 0.9 1.0 and 1.25 normal move speed
  - Guards spawn as Elite at (IWsLeft/150)% chance - 25% weaker than Double variant
  - Oppressor speed buffed halfway between normal and Double
  - Copied Brain's D2 XED_DreadHelper descriptor and wavespawner (difficulty 250 > 60) to make elim more fun
  - Salvage Changes
    - Bulks no longer have meatballs on Salvage only
    - Scan duration 2 > 1 second
    - Repair duration 10 > [10,20,30,40] seconds ByPlayerCount
      - CoopUseMultiplier = 5 (to promote teamwork)
    - Required Legs: Random between 2-5
    - Uplink/Refuel CoopUseMultiplier = 5
    - Uplink/Refuel scales @ (1.0 + ((EnemyCount - 80)/200) when > 100 enemies are alive
  - Message sends when a resup becomes available (and notes how much the next will cost)
  - Message sends when a trash breeder spawns 
  - Removed bulks from escort encounters

New changes in 3.6:
-------------------
- Revive/Regen HP - 20% + 5% per mercy stack
- Mercy Stacks accumulate every time a player downs up to 4 stacks
  Lose a stack every 30 seconds without a player down
- Treeders removed from encounters
- Treeders nerfed a bit
- Added sound cue on Treeder spawn (refinery complete sound)
- Banned warnings/anamolies
- Pitjaws unchanged (for now), only exist in Ossuary
- Scrabs promote into scrabs, grunts, and swarmers @ {50,25,25} weight
- Reduced bug speed boost during DeepScan drill portion
- Added mission start message with resupply cost info

  ",
